@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram

[*] --> StartNavigation

state StartNavigation <<choice>>
StartNavigation --> HomePage

state "HomePage" as HomePage
HomePage : entry / user is on the homepage
HomePage : do / user can navigate to projects or career opportunities
HomePage : exit / user selects a navigation option

HomePage --> ProjectSelection
HomePage --> CareerOpportunitySelection


state "Project Selection" as ProjectSelection
ProjectSelection : entry / user selects a project
ProjectSelection : do / system displays project information
ProjectSelection : exit / user chooses to view photos or videos

ProjectSelection --> ViewProjectPhotos
ProjectSelection --> ViewProjectVideos


state "Career Opportunity Selection" as CareerOpportunitySelection
CareerOpportunitySelection : entry / user selects a career opportunity
CareerOpportunitySelection : do / system displays career opportunity information
CareerOpportunitySelection : exit / user chooses to view updates or application form

CareerOpportunitySelection --> ViewCareerUpdates
CareerOpportunitySelection --> ViewCareerApplicationForm


state "View Project Photos" as ViewProjectPhotos
ViewProjectPhotos : entry / user chooses to view photos
ViewProjectPhotos : do / system displays project photos
ViewProjectPhotos : exit / user can navigate back to homepage

ViewProjectPhotos --> HomePage


state "View Project Videos" as ViewProjectVideos
ViewProjectVideos : entry / user chooses to view videos
ViewProjectVideos : do / system displays project videos
ViewProjectVideos : exit / user can navigate back to homepage

ViewProjectVideos --> HomePage


state "View Career Updates" as ViewCareerUpdates
ViewCareerUpdates : entry / user chooses to view updates
ViewCareerUpdates : do / system displays career updates
ViewCareerUpdates : exit / user can navigate back to homepage

ViewCareerUpdates --> HomePage


state "View Career Application Form" as ViewCareerApplicationForm
ViewCareerApplicationForm : entry / user chooses to view application form
ViewCareerApplicationForm : do / system displays application form
ViewCareerApplicationForm : exit / user submits application

ViewCareerApplicationForm --> SubmitApplication


state "Submit Application" as SubmitApplication
SubmitApplication : entry / user submits application
SubmitApplication : do / system checks submitted application
SubmitApplication : exit / application is either approved or rejected

SubmitApplication --> ApplicationApproved
SubmitApplication --> ApplicationRejected


state "Application Approved" as ApplicationApproved
ApplicationApproved : entry / application is approved
ApplicationApproved : do / system notifies user of approval
ApplicationApproved : exit / user can navigate back to homepage

ApplicationApproved --> HomePage


state "Application Rejected" as ApplicationRejected
ApplicationRejected : entry / application is rejected
ApplicationRejected : do / system notifies user of rejection
ApplicationRejected : exit / user can navigate back to homepage

ApplicationRejected --> HomePage


state "End" as End
End : entry / user navigates away from the system
End : exit / system ends interaction

ApplicationApproved --> End
ApplicationRejected --> End
HomePage --> End

@enduml
